==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Frett
<hw>Frett</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See 2d
<er>Fret</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Mining)</fld> <def>The worn side of the bank
of a river. See 4th <er>Fret</er>, <pos>n.</pos>, 4.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Frett</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Frett
<hw>Frett</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Frit</er>.]</ety> <def>A
vitreous compound, used by potters in glazing, consisting of lime,
silica, borax, lead, and soda.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fretted</ent>⟦br⟧
